VoiceList.Entry: “Oh,welcome home. You want dinner first? Or…” Dinner Or…
“All right,it'll be ready in no time…”
“Wh…who are you? You…can't just come barging into my home uninvited!!”
Cait Sith “Hmm,this place seems like it has a lot of secrets.”
“All right,all right. I'm making it right now.”
“…But I wonder which one is going to eat…”
“Those two…uh, Anyway,are you two friends? It really seems strange.”
“Oh man,I'm so busy. I need more help. …mummble…complain…”
“Hmm… I wonder what's going to happen now?”
“Don't worry,Mom! All of us just need to go through that door!”
“Mr. Bugenhagen sealed it so we wouldn't have to worry about it!”
“What's wrong with Bugenhagen? Is he sick?”
“No need to be sad,even if something should happen. Everything will return to the Planet…Bugenhagen says so.”
“Just the thought of something happening to Bugenhagen…worries me.”
